      "GET https://gamma-api.polymarket.com/tags (attempt 1/3)\n",
      "📌 Schema canónico construido con 12 columnas\n",
      "[tags] escribiendo filas=100 mode=overwrite\n",
      "✅ Delta Lake TAGS generado en local.\n",
      "📁 Sube esta carpeta a S3: ./polymarket/bronze/tags\n",
      "📌 Total filas tags: 100\n"
     ]
